    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. It runs well and all major mechanical systems are functioning properly. The exterior has minor signs of wear consistent with normal use \u2014 small scuffs or light scratches may be present but there are no significant dents or damage. The interior shows some use but is clean and functional overall.",
